These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different games are played: poker, billiard, scrabble, monopoly, chess, bridge
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, october, february, december, august, january
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Game   | bridge | poker  | scrabble    | monopoly  | billiard      | chess    |
| Birthday      | october  | january | august | march | december | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower, azalea, iris, dahlia, aconite
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: august, january, february, may, october, april
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who growsaconite is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | dahlia | sunflower | aconite | iris     | azalea  |
| Birthday           | february | january    | august      | april  | may | october |

