.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
House: cottage, art-deco, palace, futuristic, gothic-revival, tower
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, volleyball, water-polo, skiing, handball
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the futuristic house##1
9. the palace house is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| House   | futuristic   | tower   | gothic-revival      | art-deco | cottage  | palace   |
| Sport   | volleyball | handball | rowing | skateboarding   | skiing | water-polo |

