.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, water, soy-milk, milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, epic, sports, time-travel, comedy, drama
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Beverage   | water  | soy-milk | mirinda      | almond-milk  | iced-tea | milk |
| Movie-Genre     | satire | drama  | comedy | sports | time-travel  | epic    |

