.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
City: paris, edinburgh, colone, london, venice, new-york
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, june, july, march, february, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| City         | london | new-york | paris | venice | edinburgh | colone  |
| Birthday   | may  | march  | july  | december | february      | june |

