.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  photographer, software-developer, pilot, firefighter, writer, freelancer
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite, lemonade, milk, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the pilot##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the photographer##1
5. the person drinking milk is the freelancer##1
6. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
8. the writer is on the left of the software-developer##1
9. the freelancer is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Job   | freelancer    | pilot    | photographer | writer     | software-developer   | firefighter     |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate | cola | sprite | lemonade | almond-milk |

