.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
There 6 different types of food: cranberry, onion, orange, zucchini, banana, peach
There are 6 different nationalities: italian, british, dutch, turkish, spanish, japanese
1. the person eating orange is the spanish##1
2. the japanese is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the person eating onion##1
4. the dutch is on the right of the italian##1
5. the british is the person eating peach##1
6. the dutch is on the left of the spanish##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating peach##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Food   | peach | cranberry  | banana     | orange    | onion  | zucchini          |
| Nationality         | british  | italian | dutch | spanish | turkish | japanese |

