3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Flower    | orchid | amaryllis | daisy | zinnia    | begonia | lily      |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | bolivar     | dannemann      | siglo | dunhill           | alhambra |

