.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, august, december, march, october, january
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling, magic-tricks, hiking, reading, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Birthday          | august | january   | october  | december    | march  | july |
| Hobby   | traveling   | woodworking | fishing | reading | magic-tricks | hiking |

