.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
There 6 different types of food: spinach, apple, peas, strawberry, eggplant, potato
There are 6 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, ebony, coral, turquise, white
1. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating apple##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person who likes coral is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person eating potato##1
9. the person who likes white is on the left of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Food   | eggplant | potato | strawberry    | apple | peas  | spinach |
| Color     | azure    | turquise | coral | white   | ebony | chestnut    |

