.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, electronic, pop, punk, house
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, chaman, blend, bluemaster, cain
1. the fan of pop is the chaman-smoker##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the game-smoker##1
6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
8. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
9. the fan of house is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | gospel | punk | pop | hip-hop    | house |
| Cigar   | game   | bluemaster      | blend        | chaman    | oliveros | cain  |

