.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-14::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, climbing, surfing, cycling, lacrosse
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, amber, ivory, light-blue, aquamarine, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person who likes ivory is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |      5       |     6     |
| Sport         | swimming | cycling | water-polo | surfing | climbing | lacrosse |
| Color   | fuchsia     | amber      | light-blue    | red    | aquamarine        | ivory     |

