.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, documentary, time-travel, thriller, epic, satire
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis, swimming, lacrosse, parkour, rugby
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Movie-Genre        | time-travel     | epic | documentary   | thriller      | satire | romance |
| Sport   | lacrosse | parkour  | water-polo | tennis | swimming   | rugby     |

