.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, aristoff, prince, dunhill, chaman, game
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, soy-milk, water, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | game     | chaman       | prince  | dunhill | ritmeester    |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate  | 7up | coffee | water | milk  | soy-milk |

 